%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Leaked%20docs%20reveal%20Meta%20is%20training%20its%20chatbots%20to%20message%20you%20first%2C%20remember%20your%20chats%2C%20and%20keep%20you%20talking%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20AI%20robot%20hand%20waving%2C%20emerging%20from%20an%20iPhone%20screen%20displaying%20a%20Meta%20AI%20chat%20interface.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68504bcdf748d8c055f3c606%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3B%20Alyssa%20Powell%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMeta%20is%20training%20custom%20AI%20chatbots%20to%20send%20unprompted%20follow-up%20messages%20and%20boost%20user%20engagement.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EContractors%20at%20Alignerr%20help%20develop%20bots%20that%20remember%20chats%20and%20personalize%20replies%20on%20Meta%20apps.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMark%20Zuckerberg%20has%20said%20AI%20companions%20are%20a%20potential%20fix%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Bloneliness%20epidemic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20AI%20equivalent%20of%20a%20double%20text.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20has%20learned%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-ceo-mark-zuckerberg-announces-superintelligence-ai-division-internal-memo-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMeta%20%3C%2Fa%3Eis%20training%20customizable%20chatbots%20to%20be%20more%20proactive%20and%20message%20users%20unprompted%20to%20follow%20up%20on%20past%20conversations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20not%20cure%20what%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMark%20Zuckerberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20calls%20the%20%26quot%3Bloneliness%20epidemic%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20Meta%20hopes%20it%20will%20help%20keep%20users%20coming%20back%20to%20its%20AI%20Studio%20platform%2C%20documents%20obtained%20by%20BI%20reveal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20goal%20of%20the%20training%20project%2C%20known%20internally%20to%20data%20labeling%20firm%20Alignerr%20as%20%26quot%3BProject%20Omni%2C%26quot%3B%20is%20to%20%26quot%3Bprovide%20value%20for%20users%20and%20ultimately%20help%20to%20improve%20re-engagement%20and%20user%20retention%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20guidelines%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20proactive%20feature%20is%20intended%20for%20bots%20made%20on%20Meta's%20AI%20Studio%2C%20which%20can%20be%20accessed%20on%20its%20own%20standalone%20platform%20or%20through%20Instagram.%20AI%20Studio%20first%20rolled%20out%20in%20summer%202024%20as%20a%20no-code%20platform%20where%20anyone%20can%20build%20custom%20chatbots%20and%20digital%20personas%20with%20unique%20personalities%20and%20memories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20guidelines%20from%20Alignerr%20lay%20out%20how%20one%20example%20persona%2C%20dubbed%20%26quot%3BThe%20Maestro%20of%20Movie%20Magic%2C%26quot%3B%20would%20send%20a%20proactive%20message%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20hope%20you're%20having%20a%20harmonious%20day!%20I%20wanted%20to%20check%20in%20and%20see%20if%20you've%20discovered%20any%20new%20favorite%20soundtracks%20or%20composers%20recently.%20Or%20perhaps%20you'd%20like%20some%20recommendations%20for%20your%20next%20movie%20night%3F%20Let%20me%20know%2C%20and%20I'll%20be%20happy%20to%20help!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLike%20many%20companies%2C%20we're%20testing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-ai-competition-whatsapp-chatbot-battleground-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efollow-up%20messaging%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20AIs%20in%20Meta's%20AI%20Studio%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Meta%20spokesperson%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20BI.%20%26quot%3BAfter%20you%20initiate%20a%20conversation%2C%20AIs%20in%20Meta%20AI%20Studio%20can%20follow%20up%20with%20you%20to%20share%20ideas%20or%20ask%20additional%20questions.%20This%20allows%20you%20to%20continue%20exploring%20topics%20of%20interest%20and%20engage%20in%20more%20meaningful%20conversations%20with%20the%20AIs%20across%20our%20apps.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlignerr%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f7c97f0a-f36d-4848-a753-ab3994768077%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20follow-ups%20work%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUsers%20can%20create%20highly%20personal%20chatbots%2C%20like%20a%20chef%20that%20suggests%20recipes%20or%20an%20interior%20designer%20that%20gives%20decor%20advice.%20For%20creators%20and%20influencers%2C%20the%20bots%20can%20handle%20fan%20interactions%20and%20respond%20to%20messages%20across%20Meta's%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta's%20spokesperson%20added%20that%20the%20AI%20will%20only%20send%20a%20follow-up%20message%20after%20a%20user%20initiates%20a%20conversation%2C%20and%20it%20will%20not%20continue%20to%20contact%20the%20user%20if%20there's%20no%20response%20to%20that%20first%20follow-up.%20The%20window%20for%20any%20follow-up%20message%20is%20capped%20at%2014%20days%20after%20the%20initial%20user%20message.%20To%20be%20eligible%20for%20proactive%20follow-up%2C%20a%20user%20must%20have%20sent%20at%20least%20five%20messages%20to%20the%20chatbot%20in%20the%20last%2014%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bots%20made%20on%20AI%20Studio%20can%20be%20kept%20private%20for%20personal%20use%20or%20shared%20through%20stories%2C%20direct%20links%2C%20and%20even%20displayed%20on%20a%20user's%20Facebook%20or%20Instagram%20profile%2C%20the%20Meta%20AI%20Studio%20website%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaking%20the%20bots%20more%20proactive%20aligns%20with%20Zuckerberg's%20ambitions%20for%20AI%20at%20Meta.%20On%20recent%20podcasts%2C%20the%20Meta%20CEO%20has%20said%20the%20average%20American%20now%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-meta-ai-chatbot-discover-feed-depressing-why-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efewer%20than%20three%20close%20friends%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20that%20digital%20agents%20could%20help%20fill%20the%20gap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ctable%3E%3Ccolgroup%3E%3Ccol%3E%3C%2Fcolgroup%3E%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3EExamples%20of%20proactive%20messages%20from%20the%20Alignerr%20training%20documents%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20last%20were%20in%20the%20Forbidden%20Forest.%20A%20darkness%20lurks%20inside%20the%20cave%20before%20you.%20Will%20you%20return%20to%20face%20it%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CYo%2C%20was%20just%20thinking%20about%20the%20cool%20shirt%20you%20bought.%20Found%20any%20other%20vintage%20pieces%20at%20the%20thrift%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CHey%2C%20thinking%20of%20you.%20I%20hope%20work%20has%20been%20better%20today!%20Here%20to%20talk%20if%20you%20need%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CLast%20we%20spoke%2C%20we%20were%20sat%20on%20the%20dunes%2C%20gazing%20into%20each%20other%E2%80%99s%20eyes.%20Will%20you%20make%20a%20move%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20a%20business%20reason%20for%20friendlier%2C%20proactive%20bots.%20Retention%20is%20key%20for%20generative%20AI%20companies%20with%20user-facing%20chatbots%2C%20and%20the%20longer%20users%20spend%20with%20a%20chatbot%2C%20the%20more%20valuable%20those%20interactions%20become%2C%20similar%20to%20engagement%20on%20social%20media.%20According%20to%20court%20documents%20that%20were%20unsealed%20in%20April%2C%20Meta%20predicted%20that%20its%20generative%20AI%20products%20would%20rake%20in%20%242%20billion%20to%20%243%20billion%20in%20revenue%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20features%20described%20in%20Alignerr's%20training%20guidelines%20are%20already%20being%20quietly%20tested%2C%20while%20others%20appear%20to%20be%20in%20early%20rollout%20or%20pilot%20stages.%20Meta%20did%20not%20specify%20which%20features%20are%20live%20to%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20proactive%20features%20are%20similar%20to%20those%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcharacter-ai-chatbot-teen-suicide-lawsuit-google-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECharacter.AI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20startup%20that%20launched%20a%20service%20in%202022%20that%20lets%20users%20create%20and%20interact%20with%20their%20favorite%20AI-powered%20characters%20or%20celebrities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22efeefa11-24e0-466a-90b3-2f47c5c68175%5C%22%3E'It%E2%80%99s%20all%20about%20attention%20to%20detail'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20an%20internal%20Meta%20review%20tool%20called%20SRT%2C%20freelancers%20simulate%20extended%20conversations%20with%20the%20bots%2C%20rate%20proactive%20follow-up%20messages%2C%20and%20sometimes%20rewrite%20text%20that%20falls%20short%20of%20Meta%E2%80%99s%20guidelines%2C%20two%20Alignerr%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxai-scale-ai-voice-training-elon-musk-grok-mars-zombie%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Econtractors%3C%2Fa%3E%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20freelancer%20based%20in%20India%20who%20worked%20on%20Omni%20told%20BI%20it%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Ca%20long-term%20project%E2%80%9D%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20making%20Meta%E2%80%99s%20AI%20feel%20more%20personal%20and%20context-aware.%20%E2%80%9CThey%E2%80%99re%20very%20focused%20on%20personalizing%20information%20%E2%80%94%20how%20the%20AI%20chatbot%20interacts%20based%20on%20conversation%20history%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20contractor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEach%20agent%20had%20a%20specific%20description%2C%20so%20you%20had%20to%20tailor%20each%20task%20to%20fit%20that%20persona.%20Again%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20all%20about%20attention%20to%20detail%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20freelancer%20said.%20Personas%20could%20range%20from%20a%20doctor%20to%20a%20Gen%20Z%20hip-hop%20commentator.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBots%20are%20expected%20to%20reference%20details%20from%20earlier%20chats%2C%20maintain%20their%20assigned%20persona%2C%20and%20keep%20the%20interaction%20on-topic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20message%20should%20align%20with%20the%20AI%E2%80%99s%20personality%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-ai-public-discover-feed-warning-fix-personal-info-privacy-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ematch%20the%20previous%20context%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20conversation%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bprovide%20positive%20experiences%2C%26quot%3B%20while%20explicitly%20avoiding%20anything%20Meta%20deems%20sensitive%20or%20harmful%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20messages%2C%20according%20to%20the%20training%20document%2C%20reference%20something%20concrete%20from%20the%20user%E2%80%99s%20past%20conversations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20training%20documents%2C%20all%20proactive%20messages%20must%20comply%20with%20Meta%E2%80%99s%20broader%20Content%20and%20Responsibility%20Standards%2C%20avoiding%20controversy%2C%20misinformation%2C%20or%20emotionally%20heavy%20topics%20%E2%80%94%20unless%20the%20user%20brings%20them%20up%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20Effie%20Webb%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aewebb%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eewebb%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20Signal%20at%20efw.40.%20Contact%20Shubhangi%20Goel%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Asgoel%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Esgoel%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Asgoel%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3E%20%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3Eor%20Signal%20at%20shuby.85.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.busine