in%20Bengaluru%2C%20he%20was%20always%20inclined%20towards%20entrepreneurship%20rather%20than%20following%20the%20tech%20industry%20path%20his%20engineering%20degree%20might%20have%20suggested.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20part%20of%20my%20family%E2%80%99s%20electronics%20distribution%20business%2C%20but%20I%20never%20really%20wanted%20to%20work%20in%20that%20field%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20discovered%20that%20millet%20ice%20cream%20was%20almost%20non-existent%20in%20the%20market%2C%20I%20knew%20this%20was%20an%20opportunity%20to%20offer%20something%20different%20and%20unique%20to%20all%20dessert%20lovers%20looking%20for%20a%20healthier%20alternative.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20ice%20cream%3F%20The%20ingenious%20way%20to%20win%20over%20young%20taste%20buds%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMillets%20are%20known%20for%20being%20rich%20in%20iron%2C%20calcium%2C%20potassium%2C%20and%20other%20essential%20minerals.%20Yet%2C%20the%20entrepreneur%20noticed%20a%20common%20problem.%20%E2%80%9CChildren%20generally%20dislike%20the%20taste%20of%20millets%2C%20which%20limits%20their%20consumption.%20I%20believed%20ice%20cream%20could%20be%20a%20clever%20way%20to%20overcome%20that%20barrier.%20It%20is%20familiar%2C%20enjoyable%2C%20and%20suitable%20for%20all%20age%20groups%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20concept%20began%20to%20take%20shape%20in%202020%20when%20Gautam%20initiated%20an%20in-depth%20research%20and%20development%20journey.%20Over%20the%20following%20three%20years%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F411023%2Famit-soni-rdz-1983-bakery-food-startup-earns-national-spotlight-with-millet-cakes-cookies%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexperimented%20with%20various%20millets%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20sorghum%2C%20foxtail%2C%20pearl%2C%20and%20finger%20millet%2C%20and%20paired%20them%20with%20flavours%20such%20