%20even%20ended%20up%20feeding%20some%20failed%20batches%20to%20cows%2C%20until%20eventually%20they%20refused%20to%20eat%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20laughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20toughest%20challenges%20was%20working%20with%20millet%20milk%2C%20which%2C%20unlike%20regular%20cow%E2%80%99s%20milk%2C%20contains%20tiny%20dust%20particles.%20%E2%80%9CFiltering%20out%20these%20particles%20without%20losing%20the%20nutritional%20value%20was%20a%20major%20hurdle%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20admits.%20His%20engineering%20skills%20became%20indispensable%20as%20he%20designed%20and%20built%20a%20specialised%20machine%20to%20filter%20the%20millet%20milk%20effectively%2C%20producing%20a%20smooth%20and%20nutrient-rich%20base%20for%20the%20ice%20cream.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20entire%20process%20had%20to%20be%20invented%20from%20scratch%20as%20there%20was%20nothing%20in%20the%20market%20to%20filter%20millet%20milk%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20First%2C%20the%20naturally%20grown%20millets%20are%20sourced%20directly%20from%20local%20farmers%20and%20farmer%20producer%20organisations.%20These%20grains%20are%20carefully%20washed%20and%20dried%20to%20remove%20dust.%20The%20cleaned%20millets%20are%20then%20milled%20and%20filtered%20to%20extract%20the%20milk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENo%20artificial%20flavours%3A%20Just%20real%20fruit%2C%20real%20grain%2C%20and%20real%20effort%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20millet%20milk%20is%20prepared%2C%20it%20is%20mixed%20with%20a%20natural%20stabiliser%2C%20developed%20in-house%2C%20and%20a%20modest%20amount%20of%20sugar%2C%20usually%20between%20five%20and%2012%20percent%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20fruit%20used.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20steer%20clear%20of%20artificial%20colours%20or%20flavours.%20Every%20taste%20comes%20directly%20from%20real%20fruit%20pulp%20and%20nuts%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20making%20of%20millet%20ice%20cream%20is%20a%20meticulous%20and%20multi-step%20process.%20After%20mixing%20the%20millet%20milk%2C%20stabiliser%2C%20and%20sugar%20in%20a%20large%20tank%2C%20the%20mixture%20is%20gently%20heated%20and%20boiled%20to%20make%20sure%20it%20is%20safe%20and%20properly%20combined.%20Next%2C%20it%20undergoes%20homogenisation%20to%20break%20down%20fat%20molecules%20for%20a%20creamy%20texture%2C%20followed%20by%20pasteurisation%20to%20kill%20any%20harmful%20bacteria.%20The%20mixture%20is%20then%20aged%20for%20approximately%20eight%20hours%2C%20which%20helps%20develop%20the%20right%20consistency%20and%20flavour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-02T163702.822_11zon-1751454456.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20team%20consists%20of%20eight%20permanent%20employees%20who%20work%20in%20the%20factory%20daily%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-02T163702.822_11zon-1751454456.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-02T163702.822_11zon-1751454456-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-02T163702.822_11zon-1751454456-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-02T163702.822_11zon-1751454456-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-02T163702.822_11zon-1751454456-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-460310%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20team%20consists%20of%20eight%20permanent%20employees%20who%20work%20in%20the%20factory%20daily%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F347512%2Forder-mangoes-ratnagiri-devgadh-alphonso-jardalu-online-in-mumbai-bengaluru-delhi-pune%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFresh%20fruit%20pulp%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20added%20just%20before%20the%20ice%20cream%20goes%20into%20the%20continuous%20freezer%2C%20a%20specially%20designed%20machine%20that%20rapidly%20freezes%20the%20mixture%20while%20whipping%20it%20to%20achieve%20the%20perfect%20smoothness.%20Gautam%20and%20his%20team%20contributed%20to%20designing%20this%20machine%2C%20fine-tuning%20it%20specifically%20for%20millet-based%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20startup%20is%20winning%20over%20Bengaluru%20homes%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20officially%20launching%20Liki%20Foods%20in%202023%2C%20Gautam%20has%20expanded%20his%20range%20to%20include%20not%20only%20ice%20cream%20but%20also%20millet%20coffees%2C%20smoothies%2C%20shakes%2C%20rusks%2C%20cookies%2C%20sandwiches%2C%20and%20even%20pasta%20dishes.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20prove%20that%20millets%20can%20be%20enjoyed%20in%20many%20familiar%20and%20innovative%20forms%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20response%20from%20customers%20has%20also%20been%20encouraging%20so%20far.%20Dr%20Bharti%2C%20a%20Bengaluru%20resident%20and%20a%20long-time%20supporter%20of%20the%20brand%2C%20shares%20how%20she%20discovered%20Liki%20Foods.%20%E2%80%9CI%20found%20out%20about%20it%20through%20my%20son%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20brought%20home%20a%20tub%20one%20day%2C%20and%20we%20were%20all%20surprised%20by%20how%20good%20it%20tasted.%20Since%20then%2C%20it%20has%20become%20a%20regular%20treat%20in%20our%20household.%E2%80%