y%20general%20said%20that%20Ukraine%20needs%20all%20the%20help%20that%20it%20can%20get.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20is%20halting%20the%20delivery%20of%20ammunition%20to%20Ukraine%2C%20and%20reports%20indicate%20that%20some%20of%20the%20most%20effective%20and%20necessary%20American%20weapons%20the%20country%20has%20received%20could%20be%20affected.%20Ukraine%20says%20it%20is%20working%20to%20get%20answers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHits%20to%20air%20defense%20interceptor%20capacity%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20could%20hinder%20its%20strained%20batteries%20at%20a%20moment%20when%20Russia%20is%20ramping%20up%20its%20attacks.%20Over%20the%20weekend%2C%20it%20struck%20Ukraine%20with%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20bombardments%20of%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20to%20cancel%20a%20shipment%20of%20weapons%20and%20ammo%20that%20had%20been%20promised%20by%20the%20Biden%20administration%20was%20confirmed%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhite%20House%20Deputy%20Press%20Secretary%20Anna%20Kelly%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20%26quot%3Bthis%20decision%20was%20made%20to%20put%20America's%20interests%20first%20following%20a%20DoD%20%5BDepartment%20of%20Defense%5D%20review%20of%20our%20nation's%20military%20support%20and%20assistance%20to%20other%20countries%20across%20the%20globe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20strength%20of%20the%20United%20States%20Armed%20Forces%20remains%20unquestioned%20%E2%80%94%20just%20ask%20Iran.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENews%20on%20the%20decision%20was%20first%20reported%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnews%2F2025%2F07%2F01%2Fpentagon-munitions-ukraine-halt-00436048%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPolitico%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20said%20that%20it%20came%20after%20the%20Pentagon%20reviewed%20its%20stockpiles%20and%20expressed%20concern%20that%20some%20critical%20munitions%20were%20in%20dwindling%20supply%2C%20raising%20questions%20about%20US%20readiness.%20The%20Pentagon%20