mpacted%2C%20including%20howitzers%2C%20Patriots%2C%20and%20HIMARS%2C%20systems%20that%20have%20been%20critical%20in%20this%20war.%20The%20air%20defenses%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20have%20been%20critical%20in%20shielding%20Ukraine's%20cities%20from%20Russian%20missile%20strikes.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%20said%20Wednesday%20that%20officials%20are%20clarifying%20the%20changes%20with%20their%20US%20counterparts%2C%20and%20stressed%20the%20importance%20of%20air%20defenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20acknowledged%20at%20the%20annual%20NATO%20summit%20last%20week%20that%20Ukraine%20wanted%20more%20Patriot%20interceptors%20and%20said%20the%20US%20would%20%26quot%3Bsee%20if%20we%20can%20make%20some%20available%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20he%20cautioned%20that%20%26quot%3Bthey're%20very%20hard%20to%20get.%20We%20need%20them%2C%20too.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-patriots-protect-kyiv-europe-allies-no-strong-replacement-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUS-made%20M1M-104%20Patriot%20surface-to-air%20missile%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20manufactured%20primarily%20by%20Raytheon%20and%20Lockheed%20Martin%2C%20has%20been%20key%20to%20protecting%20Ukraine%20from%20Russian%20missile%20strikes%20since%20Kyiv%20first%20received%20it%20two%20years%20ago.%20Ukraine%20now%20reportedly%20operates%20six%20Patriots%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20countries%2C%20like%20Germany%20and%20the%20Netherlands%2C%20have%20also%20provided%20Patriots%20and%20could%20potentially%20provide%20interceptors.%20Ukraine%20has%20said%20it's%20running%20low%20on%20the%20interceptors%2C%20meaning%20the%20delay%20of%20further%20supplies%20from%20the%20US%20could%20be%20detrimental.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPatriot%20systems%20are%20vital%20to%20Ukraine's%20ability%20to%20defend%20against%20Russian%20ballistic%20missile%20strikes%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20DC-based%20think%20tank%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22htt