u%20feel%20good%20so%20you%20can%20relax%20and%20be%20in%20the%20moment%20when%20you're%20at%20your%20reunion%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.drpatricelegoy.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPatrice%20Le%20Goy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20psychologist%20and%20licensed%20marriage%20and%20family%20therapist%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20some%20people%2C%20it%20will%20be%20important%20to%20have%20accomplishments%20to%20share%2C%20and%20for%20others%2C%20it%20will%20be%20having%20that%20perfect%20outfit%20picked%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20don't%20want%20to%20sound%20rehearsed%2C%20but%20it%20might%20help%20to%20have%20a%20script%20or%20a%20few%20life%20updates%20in%20mind%2C%20especially%20if%20you%20tend%20to%20overshare%20or%20get%20nervous%20in%20social%20settings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2222a33347-010c-4307-9b2f-95ce11e826b7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon't%3A%20Gossip%20about%20people%20or%20their%20appearance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20conversation%20stalls%2C%20it%20can%20be%20tempting%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgossip-vs-venting-therapist-explains-difference-between-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eengage%20in%20gossip%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BYou%20may%20regret%20it%20if%20you%20use%20this%20time%20to%20speak%20badly%20about%20people%20you%20haven't%20seen%20in%20a%20long%20time%2C%20especially%20if%20it%20gets%20back%20to%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Le%20Goy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20visual%20creatures%2C%20we%20tend%20to%20notice%20people's%20appearance%2C%20especially%20if%20they%20look%20different%20from%20how%20we%20remember%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20making%20comments%20about%20someone's%20body%2C%20even%20if%20you%20believe%20you're%20giving%20a%20compliment%2C%20can%20trigger%20people%20and%20make%20them%20feel%20self-conscious%2C%26quot%3B%20Moore%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223b21a706-6992-48b