y%20cuts%20salespeople%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Microsoft%20Chief%20Commercial%20Officer%20Judson%20Althoff%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F680bfb1c3fe8d39283642855%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22533%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMicrosoft%20Chief%20Commercial%20Officer%20Judson%20Althoff.%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMicrosoft's%20Judson%20Althoff%20wants%20to%20revamp%20sales%20to%20become%20the%20%26quot%3Bfrontier%20AI%20firm%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20memo%20shows.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20changes%20come%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-layoffs-major-round-managers-workers-2025-7%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMicrosoft%20cuts%20thousands%20of%20roles%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20in%20sales.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAlthoff's%20memo%20outlined%20the%20changes%20to%20the%20organization%20and%20his%20ambitions%20for%20the%20new%20fiscal%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft's%20sales%20chief%2C%20Judson%20Althoff%2C%20is%20revamping%20his%20unit%20to%20make%20it%20more%20AI-focused%2C%20according%20to%20an%20internal%20memo%20viewed%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthoff%2C%20the%20company's%20chief%20commercial%20officer%2C%20sent%20the%20memo%20to%20the%20sales%20unit%2C%20called%20Microsoft%20Customer%20and%20Partner%20Solutions%20(MCAPS)%2C%20a%20day%20before%20the%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-layoffs-major-round-managers-workers-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eannounced%20a%20significant%20round%20of%20layoffs.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20layoffs%20affected%20many%20salespeople%20in%20Althoff's%20organization%2C%20sources%20familiar%20with%20them%20said.%20The%20memo%20did%20not%20mention%20the%20layoffs%2C%20announced%20beginning%20July%202%20in%20separate%20communications%20to%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthoff's%20memo%20called%20for%20%26quot%3Bcontinued%20agility%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Breinventing%20Microsoft%20and%20MCAPS%26quot%3B%20to%20become%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Frontier%20AI%20Firm%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20outlined%20the%20five%20priorities%20of%20the%20sales%20organization%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cem%3EEstablish%20a%20Copilot%20on%20every%20device%20and%20across%20every%20role%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cem%3EStrengthen%20our%20M365%20and%20D365%20execution%20and%20penetration%20across%20all%20segments%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cem%3ECreate%20meaningful%20AI%20design%20wins%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cem%3EGrow%20our%20cloud%20platform%20business%20by%20migrating%20and%20modernizing%20workloads%20to%20Azure%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cem%3EBuild%20a%20cybersecurity%20foundation%20to%20enable%20secure%20AI%20Transformation%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Cp%3EAlthoff%20in%20April%20unveiled%20plans%20to%20slash%20the%20number%20of%20the%20sales%20team's%20%26quot%3Bsolutions%20areas%26quot%3B%20by%20half%20during%20the%20next%20fiscal%20year%2C%20which%20started%20July%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20obtained%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-consolidate-teams-simplify-ai-copilot-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecopies%20of%20slides%20from%20Althoff's%20April%20presentation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20showing%20the%20company%20planned%20to%20condense%20its%20six%20previous%20areas%20into%20three%3A%20AI%20Business%20Solutions%2C%20Cloud%20%26amp%3B%20AI%20Platforms%2C%20and%20Security%2C%20according%20to%20those%20slides.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20Business%20Solutions%20will%20focus%20on%20getting%20%26quot%3BCopilots%20on%20every%20device%20across%20every%20role%26quot%3B%20and%20on%20selling%20Microsoft%20365's%20suite%20of%20business%20applications%20and%20Dynamics%20365%20customer%20relationship%20management%20service%2C%20according%20to%20the%20July%201%20memo.