%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20former%20president%20spoke%20at%20the%20Society%20for%20Human%20Resource%20Management%20conference%20in%20San%20Diego.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BIn%20a%20sense%2C%20the%20president%20of%20the%20United%20States%20is%20the%20chief%20people%20officer%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBiden%20stressed%20that%20leaders%20should%20encourage%20employees%20to%20take%20time%20off%20to%20meet%20family%20obligations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EJoe%20Biden%20told%20a%20group%20of%20human-resources%20professionals%20Wednesday%20that%20the%20president%20of%20the%20U.S.%20is%20in%20a%20sense%20the%20nation's%20chief%20people%20officer%20before%20passing%20on%20leadership%20lessons%20he%20gleaned%20throughout%20his%20decades-long%20career%20in%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20in%20San%20Diego%20to%20members%20of%20the%20Society%20for%20Human%20Resource%20Management%20at%20the%20trade%20group's%20annual%20conference%2C%20the%20former%20commander-in-chief%20emphasized%20the%20importance%20for%20leaders%20to%20treat%20all%20employees%20with%20respect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fab288ea-4050-41ba-8d56-cd5dbecd5917%5C%22%3E'Leadership%20is%20all%20about%20getting%20personal'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20job%20is%20about%20a%20lot%20more%20than%20a%20paycheck.%20It's%20about%20your%20dignity%2C%26quot%3B%20Biden%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20a%20lesson%20he%20received%20early%20in%20life%20from%20his%20father.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20that%20lesson%20has%20guided%20my%20whole%20career%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20president%20also%20stressed%20that%20leaders%20should%20recognize%20that%20family%20matters%20to%20employees%20%E2%80%94%20and%20to%20encourage%20employees%20to%20not%20be%20afraid%20to%20take%20time%20off%20from%20work%20to%20meet%20family%20obligations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToo%20often%20we%20try%20to%20separate%20people%20into%20categories%20of%20their%20work%20and%20their%20family.%20We%20say%20it's%20business%2C%20it's%20not%20personal%2C%26quot%3B%20Biden%20told%20the%20audience.%20%26quot%3BLeadership%20is%20all%20about%20getting%20personal.%20%E2%80%A6%20It's%20about%20connecting.%20It%20means%20having%20empathy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20was%20vice%20president%2C%20Biden%20said%20he%20sent%20a%20memo%20to%20White%20House%20staff%20to%20make%20sure%20they%20knew%20where%20he%20stood%20on%20the%20matter.%20In%20the%20memo%20he%20encouraged%20them%20to%20prioritize%20important%20dates%20in%20their%20loved%20one's%20lives%20such%20as%20birthdays%2C%20weddings%2C%20and%20graduations%20over%20work.%20And%20he%20said%20he'd%20be%20disappointed%20if%20they%20didn't%20heed%20his%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBiden%20acknowledged%20that%20it%20can%20be%20hard%20for%20people%20to%20set%20aside%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20tell%20ourselves%2C%20'I%20have%20to%20be%20at%20that%20meeting.%20I%20have%20to%20get%20that%20report%20done.%20I%20have%20to%20take%20that%20trip%2C'%20%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Biden%2C%20who%20lost%20his%20first%20wife%20and%20daughter%20in%20a%20car%20accident%20in%201972%2C%20emphasized%20that%20this%20kind%20of%20thinking%20can%20be%20a%20mistake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20moments%20you'll%20never%20get%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22802fdb9f-17f9-40f4-b8d5-ddc7c6989977%5C%22%3E'Keep%20helping%20people%20get%20back%20up'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20Biden%20argued%20that%20leadership%20is%20about%20sharing%20credit%2C%20giving%20recognition%2C%20and%20being%20willing%20to%20risk%20losing%20your%20job%20if%20it%20means%20doing%20the%20right%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20some%20point%20in%20our%20lives%2C%20in%20ways%20large%20and%20small%2C%20all%20of%20us%20are%20called%20upon%20to%20show%20bravery%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBiden%20closed%20out%20his%20remarks%20by%20encouraging%20the%20audience%20of%20HR%20professiona