o%20think%20%5Bformer%20Washington%20Post%20publisher%5D%20Katharine%20Graham%20wouldn't%20have%20done%20it.%20We%20don't%20know%20anything%20about%20%5BDavid%5D%20Ellison.%20He%20might%20be%20a%20terrific%20supporter%20of%20newsgathering%2C%20but%20one%20has%20become%20pessimistic%20with%20these%20issues.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2208b0de1b-ea65-45b6-8cd7-096513412d1d%5C%22%3ESen.%20Elizabeth%20Warren%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20Paramount%20folding%20to%20Donald%20Trump%20at%20the%20same%20time%20the%20company%20needs%20his%20administration's%20approval%20for%20its%20billion-dollar%20merger%2C%20this%20could%20be%20bribery%20in%20plain%20sight.%20Paramount%20has%20refused%20to%20provide%20answers%20to%20a%20congressional%20inquiry%2C%20so%20I'm%20calling%20for%20a%20full%20investigation%20into%20whether%20or%20not%20any%20anti-bribery%20laws%20were%20broken.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20settlement%20exposes%20a%20glaring%20need%20for%20rules%20to%20restrict%20donations%20to%20sitting%20presidents'%20libraries.%20I%20will%20soon%20introduce%20new%20legislation%20to%20rein%20in%20corruption%20through%20presidential%20library%20donations.%20The%20Trump%20administration's%20level%20of%20sheer%20corruption%20is%20appalling%20and%20Paramount%20should%20be%20ashamed%20of%20putting%20its%20profits%20over%20independent%20journalism.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22marty%20baron%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68655fa485e81483682d3b8c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMarty%20Baron%2C%20the%20former%20Washington%20Post%20executive%20editor%2C%20says%20the%20'bigger%20issue'%20will%20be%20CBS%20News'%20new%20owners.%3Cp%3EFrancine%20Orr%20%2F%20Los%20Angeles%20Times%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224c7ee0b7-6a07-4193-9e3d-4264f17cc786%5C%22%3EMarty%20Baron%2C%20former%20Washington%20Post%20executive%20editor%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAssuming%20the%20merger%20gets%20approved%2C%20the%20bigger%20issue%20will%20be%20the%20posture%20of%20new%20owners%20toward%20'60%20Minutes'%20and%20really%20all%20of%20CBS%20News.%20I%20would%20hope%20for%20respect%20for%20the%20network's%20heritage%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20pledge%20of%20journalistic%20independence%20and%20proof%20that%20they%20will%20honor%20it.%20The%20early%20indicators%20aren't%20all%20that%20encouraging.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e7e70809-dd20-4293-982e-38adabe04a5b%5C%22%3ETim%20Richardson%2C%20journalism%20and%20disinformation%20program%20director%20at%20PEN%20America%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BParamount's%20decision%20to%20settle%20a%20meritless%20lawsuit%20rather%20than%20stand%20behind%20its%20journalists%20at%20CBS%20News%20is%20a%20spineless%20capitulation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20was%20a%20moment%20to%20defend%20press%20freedom%20and%20support%20reporters%20targeted%20by%20a%20frivolous%20legal%20attack.%20Instead%2C%20Paramount%20chose%20appeasement%20to%20bolster%20its%20finances%2C%20sending%20a%20dangerous%20message%20that%20media%20outlets%20can%20be%20pressured%20into%20submission%20if%20corporate%20parents%20find%20their%20profits%20at%20risk%20from%20government%20action%20in%20unrelated%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20two%20major%20network%20owners%20bowing%20to%20the%20president%20in%20quick%20succession%2C%20the%20danger%20is%20clear%3A%20emboldened%20politicians%20and%20powerful%20actors%20will%20feel%20more%20free%20than%20ever%20to%20weaponize%20lawsuits%20and%20bring%20regulatory%20pressure%20to%20bear%20to%20silence%20and%20censor%20independent%20journalism.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fce69d6c-739c-4c42-86d4-c3d9179e3e4f%5C%22%3ERaymond%20James%20analysts%20Ric%20Prentiss%20and%20Brent%20Penter%20(in%20a%20note%20to%20clients)%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20with%20the%20lawsuit%20settled%2C%20we%20believe%20the%20FCC%20is%20poised%20to%20approve%20the%20PARA%2FSkydance%20deal%2C%20and%20we%20feel%20the%20deal%20can%20close%20within%20a%20couple%20of%20weeks%20after%20FCC%20approval.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20expectation%20has%20been%20a%20closing%20(with%20no%20material%20changes%20to%20terms)%20after%201H25%20but%20still%20in%20the%20summer%2C%20and%20we%20feel%20that%20continues%20to%20be%20the%20case.%20We%20think%20companies%2C%20and%20especially%20CFOs%2C%20like%20to%20close%20deals%20on%20the%20first%20day%20of%20a%20month%20(with%20the%20first%20day%20of%20a%20quarter%20even%20more%20preferred%2C%20but%20missed%207%2F1%20in%20this%20case).%20And%20we%20expect%20PARA%20to%20be%20ready%20to%20close%20this%20chapter%20of%20its%20story%20soon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224853ba28-cf81-4e2f-8c76-d36af2ebe803%5C%22%3EPeter%20Kafka%2C%20Business%20Insider%20chief%20correspondent%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20deal%20we%20thought%20we'd%20see%20back%20in%20January%3A%20A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-meta-paramount-trump-lawsuit-settle-gannett-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ETrump-friendly%20media%20mogul%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20agrees%20to%20pay%20him%20millions%20of%20dollars%2C%20so%20she%20can%20sell%20her%20company%20to%20a%20Trump-backing%20tech%20mogul.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20you%20can%20squint%20and%20argue%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fpkafka%2Fstatus%2F1940273632254799883%3Fs%3D46%26t%3DxhuXMba3HM4poWm9CQq-PA%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EParamount%20is%20a%20winner%20here%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20it%20didn't%20have%20to%20give%20up%20more%20%E2%80%94%20like%20a%20public%20apology%20for%20something%20it%20didn't%20do.%20All%20it%20had%20to%20do%20is%20fork%20over%20the%20now-standard%20payment%20for%20media%20and%20tech%20companies%20that%20want%20to%20operate%20in%20Trump%202.0.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20the%20other%20hand%3A%20These%20corporate%20payoffs%20to%20the%20president%20of%20the%20United%20States%20%3Cem%3Eshould%3C%2Fem%3E%20be%20shocking.%20My%20worry%20is%20that%20we're%20just%20a%20few%20months%20into%20this%2C%20and%20we've%20already%20accepted%20them%20as%20normal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223e5d7f8e-0506-4041-ae06-64fb329bc48b%5C%22%3EClayton%20Weimers%2C%20executive%20director%20of%20Reporters%20without%20Borders%20USA%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20shameful%20decision%20by%20Paramount.%20Shari%20Redstone%20and%20Paramount's%20board%20should%20have%20stood%20by%20CBS%20journalists%20and%20the%20integrity%20of%20press%20freedom.%20Instead%2C%20they%20chose%20to%20reward%20Donald%20Trump%20for%20his%20petty%20legal%20assault%20against%20both.%20A%20line%20is%20being%20drawn%20between%20the%20owners%20of%20American%20news%20media%20who%20are%20willing%20to%20stand%20up%20for%20press%20freedom%20and%20those%20who%20capitulate%20to%20the%20demands%20of%20the%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20Paramount's%20leaders%20chose%20to%20be%20on%20the%20wrong%20side%20of%20that%20dividing%20line%2C%20but%20they'd%20be%20mistaken%20to%20believe%20appeasing%20Trump%20today%20will%20stop%20his%20attacks%20in%20the%20future.%20News%20media%20owners%20are%20much%20better%20off%20standing%20strong%20than%20acquiescing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22df07cd8d-9d10-424c-b11c-fc7bf8a26939%5C%22%3EJeff%20Greenfield%2C%20former%20CBS%20senior%20political%20correspondent%2C%20on%20X%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWill%20this%20encourage%20politicians%20and%20others%20to%20file%20bogus%20lawsuits%20%5Ba%5Ds%20a%20way%20of%20intimidating%20news%20organizations%20and%20their%20corporate%20boards%3F%20Will%20the%20correspondents%20and%20producers%20of%20%26quot%3B60%20Minutes%26quot%3B%20see%20this%20as%20a%20corporate%20betrayal%20of%20the%20program%20in%20service%20to%20a%20multi%20billion%20dollar%20merger%3F%20(Answers%20to%20both%20questions%3A%20YES.)%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a5adb4ff-f626-44f5-a697-7b374e473782%5C%22%3ESen.%20Bernie%20Sanders%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20decision%20by%20the%20Redstone%20family%2C%20the%20major%20owners%20of%20Paramount%2C%20to%20settle%20a%20bogus%20lawsuit%20with%20President%20Trump%20over%20a%2060%20Minutes%20report%20he%20did%20not%20like%20is%20an%20extremely%20dangerous%20precedent%20in%20terms%20of%20both%20the%20first%20amendment%20and%20government%20extortion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BParamount's%20decision%20will%20only%20embolden%20Trump%20to%20continue%20attacking%2C%20suing%20and%20intimidating%20the%20media%20which%20he%20has%20labeled%20'the%20enemy%20of%20the%20people.'%20It%20is%20a%20dark%20day%20for%20independent%20journalism%20and%20freedom%20of%20the%20press%20-%20an%20essential%20part%20of%20our%20democracy.%20It%20is%20a%20victory%20for%20a%20president%20who%20is%20attempting%20to%20stifle%20dissent%20and%20undermine%20American%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20pretty%20obvious%20why%20Paramount%20chose%20to%20surrender%20to%20Trump.%20The%20Redstone%20family%20is%20in%20line%20to%20receive%20%242.4%20billion%20from%20the%20sale%20of%20Paramount%20to%20Skydance%2C%20but%20they%20can%20only%20receive%20this%20money%20if%20the%20Trump%20administration%20approves%20this%20deal.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20the%20Redstone%20family%20diminished%20the%20freedom%20of%20the%20press%20today%20in%20exchange%20for%20a%20%242.4%20billion%20payday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMake%20no%20mistake%20about%20it.%20Trump%20is%20undermining%20our%20democracy%20and%20rapidly%20moving%20us%20towards%20authoritarianism%20and%20the%20billionaires%20who%20care%20more%20about%20their%20stock%20portfolios%20than%20our%20democracy%20are%20helping%20him%20do%20it.%20That%20is%20beyond%20unacceptable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b9be6a1b-d7f7-425d-9b85-7bdb639c03fd%5C%22%3EJonathan%20Miller%2C%20chief%20executive%20of%20Integrated%20Media%2C%20which%20specializes%20in%20digital%20media%20investments%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20there%20was%20no%20apology%20was%20good%2C%20and%20it%20makes%20sense%20in%20the%20grand%20scheme%20of%20things%20in%20what%20they%20have%20to%20do.%20It's%20pretty%20hard%20to%20escape%20the%20idea%20that%20it's%20political.%20The%20Ellisons%20stayed%20away%20from%20any%20political%20statement%20during%20the%20whole%20process%20%E2%80%94%20now%20we'll%20see%20what%20they%20do.%20And%20there's%20obviously%20a%20job%20open%20at%20CBS%20News%20they'll%20have%20to%20fill.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22370f4867-9813-4877-a96f-e4ad3667518a%5C%22%3ERome%20Hartman%2C%20veteran%20former%20'60%20Minutes'%20producer%2C%20including%20on%20the%20Kamala%20Harris%20segment%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20settlement%20is%20a%20cowardly%20capitulation%20by%20the%20corporate%20leaders%20of%20Paramount%2C%20and%20a%20fundamental%20betrayal%20of%20'60%20Minutes'%20and%20CBS%20News.%20The%20story%20that%20was%20the%20subject%20of%20this%20lawsuit%20was%20edited%20by%20the%20book%20and%20in%20accordance%20with%20CBS%20News%20standards.%20Our%20corporate%20bosses%20know%20that%3B%20they%20know%20that%20this%20lawsuit%20is%20completely%20baseless.%20But%20they%20settled%20it%20in%20order%20to%20preserve%20Shari%20Redstone's%20payday.%20That%20is%20shameful.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c821f598-19a3-4567-9dd1-81743b4522a4%5C%22%3EJohn%20Harwood%2C%20veteran%20White%20House%20correspondent%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20hard%20to%20say%20which%20is%20worse%3A%20the%20craven%20surrender%20by%20a%20media%20company%20that%20did%20nothing%20wrong%2C%20the%20betrayal%20of%20one%20of%20our%20finest%20news%20outlets%2C%20or%20the%20lawless%20extortion%20by%20the%20President%20of%20the%20United%20States.%20that%20it%20all%20happened%20in%20broad%20daylight%20is%20an%20appalling%20measure%20of%20the%20damage%20Trump%20has%20inflicted.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22151c8c5a-e11b-43ca-a937-a216a50713aa%5C%22%3EJill%20Abramson%2C%20former%20executive%20editor%20of%20The%20New%20York%20Times%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20look%20at%20the%20journalism%20consequences%2C%20which%20I%20think%20are%20serious.%20How%20can%20you%20really%20fulfill%20the%20press's%20mission%20as%20the%20people%20who%20guard%20against%20autocracy%20and%20make%20sure%20the%20government%20is%20functioning%20as%20it%20should%3F%20The%20networks%20aren't%20as%20powerful%20as%20they%20once%20were%2C%20but%20are%20still%20important%20news%20organizations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20easy%20for%20me%20to%20say%20this%20but%3A%20Just%20do%20the%20work%20that%20made%20the%20First%20Amendment%20first%20and%20gave%20the%20press%20a%20lot%20of%20freedom%20and%20leeway.%20Don't%20be%20cowed%20by%20the%20Trump%20White%20House.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2265a1cf60-496b-4048-a849-20c977e8c59d%5C%22%3EFull%20Paramount%20and%20Trump%20team%20statements%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20Paramount%20Global's%20statement%3A%20%26quot%3BCompanies%20often%20settle%20litigation%20to%20avoid%20the%20high%20and%20somewhat%20unpredictable%20costs%20of%20legal%20defense%2C%20the%20risk%20of%20an%20adverse%20judgment%20that%20could%20result%20in%20significant%20financial%20or%20reputational%20damage%2C%20and%20the%20disruption%20to%20business%20operations%20that%20prolonged%20legal%20battles%20can%20cause.%20Settlement%20offers%20a%20negotiated%20resolution%20that%20allows%20companies%20to%20focus%20on%20their%20core%20objectives%20rather%20than%20being%20mired%20in%20uncertainty%20and%20distraction.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20here's%20Trump's%20legal%20team's%3A%20%26quot%3BWith%20this%20record%20settlement%2C%20President%20Donald%20J.%20Trump%20delivers%20another%20win%20for%20the%20American%20people%20as%20he%2C%20once%20again%2C%20holds%20the%20Fake%20News%20media%20accountable%20for%20their%20wrongdoing%20and%20deceit.%20CBS%20and%20Paramount%20Global%20realized%20the%20strength%20of%20this%20historic%20case%20and%20had%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20settle.%20President%20Trump%20will%20always%20ensure%20that%20no%20one%20gets%20away%20with%20lying%20to%20the%20American%20People%20as%20he%20continues%20on%20his%20singular%20mission%20to%20Make%20America%20Great%20Again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparamount-trump-settlement-media-politics-reactions-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751483464000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686557ab3d5881a51c1c8b4b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparamount-trump-settlement-media-politics-reactions-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Media%20and%20political%20insiders%20react%20to%20Paramount's%20settlement%20with%20Trump%2C%20questioning%20its%20potential%20impacts%20on%20the%20Skydance%20merger%20and%20press%20freedom.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lmoses%40insider.com%20(Lucia%20Moses%2CLara%20O'Reilly)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A32%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparamount-trump-settlement-media-politics-reactions-2025-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'May%20Miss%20Crores%20Of%20Names'%3A%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%20Over%20'Rushed'%20Bihar%20Poll%20Roll%20Revision%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Ciframe%20data-src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fembed-player%2Fid%2F960633%2Fplay-via-app-wap%3FpWidth%3D100%26amp%3BpHeight%3D100%26amp%3Bembed_type%3Dstory%26amp%3Bsite%3Dclassic%26amp%3Bautostart%3D1%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22about%3Ablank%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223