2%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Escore%20well%20in%20Geography%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20despite%20considerable%20effort%20and%20time%20invested%2C%20prompted%20him%20to%20consider%20switching%20his%20optional%20to%20Anthropology%2C%20a%20decision%20that%20ultimately%20proved%20to%20be%20beneficial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20the%20year%202023%2C%20and%20Ajay%20found%20himself%20standing%20at%20a%20crossroads%20in%20his%20UPSC%20journey.%20Four%20attempts%20behind%20him%2C%20yet%20success%20had%20eluded%20him%20so%20far.%20As%20he%20prepared%20for%20his%20fifth%20attempt%2C%20a%20persistent%20dilemma%20clouded%20his%20thoughts%3A%20%E2%80%9CShould%20I%20change%20my%20optional%20subject%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20longest%20time%2C%20Geography%20had%20been%20his%20chosen%20path.%20Many%20found%20success%20with%20it%2C%20but%20for%20Ajay%2C%20it%20was%20a%20struggle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDespite%20my%20best%20efforts%2C%20Geography%20seemed%20like%20a%20distant%20land%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20conquer.%20Every%20attempt%20in%20the%20UPSC%20mains%20ended%20with%20the%20same%20result%2C%20setbacks%20and%20a%20nagging%20sense%20that%20I%20was%20missing%20something%20essential%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20more%20than%20a%20year%2C%20Ajay%20wrestled%20with%20this%20decision.%20%E2%80%9CDoubts%20gnawed%20at%20me%2C%20and%20peers%20discouraged%20any%20thoughts%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fweb-stories%2Fupsc-cse-2024-how-to-choose-optional-subject-ias-irs-ips-civil-servants-share-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eswitching%20my%20optional%20subject%20%3C%2Fa%3Eat%20the%20last%20moment.%20After%20all%2C%20I%20spent%20four%20years%20preparing%20it%20and%20changing%20subjects%20isn%E2%80%99t%20advisable.%20Yet%2C%20deep%20down%2C%20I%20knew%20it%20was%20draining%20my%20potential.%20This%20was%20very%20clear%20in%20my%20scores.%20No%20matter%20how%20muc