20of%20revising%20at%20least%20twice%20between%20the%20prelims%20and%20mains.%20A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F307829%2Frevision-tips-for-upsc-cse-mains-optional-subject-by-ias-officer-akshita-gupta%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estrategic%20third%20revision%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewas%20done%20right%20after%20finishing%20the%20General%20Studies%20papers%2C%20taking%20advantage%20of%20the%20five-day%20gap%20before%20the%20optional%20exams.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20timing%20was%20key%20to%20maintaining%20freshness%20in%20concepts%20and%20keeping%20them%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20my%20mind%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FAjay-IRS-upsc-cse-1-1751458735.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22This%20year%2C%20Ajay%20successfully%20cleared%20the%20prestigious%20UPSC%20CSE%2C%20securing%20an%20All%20India%20Rank%20of%20705.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FAjay-IRS-upsc-cse-1-1751458735.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FAjay-IRS-upsc-cse-1-1751458735-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FAjay-IRS-upsc-cse-1-1751458735-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FAjay-IRS-upsc-cse-1-1751458735-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FAjay-IRS-upsc-cse-1-1751458735-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-460385%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThis%20year%2C%20Ajay%20successfully%20cleared%20the%20prestigious%20UPSC%20CSE%2C%20securing%20an%20All%20India%20Rank%20of%20705.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3)%20Concise%20note-making%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECrafting%20concise%20notes%20was%20crucial.%20Ajay%20emphasises%20making%20brief%2C%20to-the-point%20notes%20that%20encapsulate%20the%20essence%20of%20the%20topics%2C%20ensuring%20that%20complex%20information%20can%20be%20quickly%20recalled.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20where%20I%20was%20lagging%20in%20Geography%20in%20the%20first%20place.%20I%20made%20the%20mistake%20of%20not%20making%20concise%20notes%2C%20and%20at%20the%20end%2C%20I%20had%20massive%20and%20cluttered%20notes%2C%20which%20made%20it%20difficult%20for%20me%20to%20revise%20the%20concepts.%20This%20time%2C%20I%20learnt%20my%20lesson%20and%20prepared%20clear%20notes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4)%20Practice%20with%20previous%20year%20questions%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjay%20consistently%20practiced%20the%20previous%2010%20years%E2%80%99%20question%20papers%20multiple%20times%20to%20sharpen%20his%20answer-writing%20skills%20and%20get%20himself%20accustomed%20to%20the%20exam%20pattern.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20practice%20not%20only%20familiarised%20me%20with%20the%20exam%20pattern%20but%20also%20honed%20my%20real-time%20answer%20writing%20abilities%2C%20which%20is%20crucial%20for%20performing%20well%20in%20the%20mains%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E5)%20Value%20addition%20through%20case%20studies%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECollecting%20case%20studies%20and%20integrating%20them%20into%20his%20answers%20was%20a%20strategy%20Ajay%20used%20to%20add%20depth%20and%20differentiate%20his%20answers%20in%20optional%20papers%20from%20General%20Studies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20made%20a%20conscious%20effort%20to%20understand%20where%20and%20how%20to%20apply%20anthropological%20theories%20in%20different%20contexts.%20This%20involved%20thinking%20about%20possible%20scenarios%20and