n%20opportunity%20for%20farmers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHigh-Value%20Crop%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Geranium%20offers%20a%20significant%20income%20opportunity%20for%20farmers%20due%20to%20its%20high%20market%20value.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMultiple%20Oil%20Sources%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Oil%20can%20be%20easily%20extracted%20from%20the%20plant%E2%80%99s%20%3Cstrong%3Estems%2C%20leaves%2C%20and%20flowers%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ELong-Term%20Yield%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Once%20planted%2C%20geranium%20can%20be%20harvested%20for%20%3Cstrong%3Ethree%20to%20four%20years%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20reducing%20replanting%20costs.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ELow%20Maintenance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20The%20plant%20requires%20%3Cstrong%3Eminimal%20pesticide%20use%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20as%20it%20is%20naturally%20%3Cstrong%3Eresistant%20to%20pests%20and%20grazing%20animals%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHigher%20Returns%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Yields%20%3Cstrong%3Emuch%20higher%20profits%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20compared%20to%20many%20traditional%20crops.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESustainable%20Livelihood%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Promoting%20geranium%20farming%20could%20help%20farmers%20%3Cstrong%3Eincrease%20income%20and%20financial%20stability%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGeranium%20was%20first%20introduced%20in%20the%20temperate%20regions%20of%20South%20India%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20Nilgiris%20(Tamil%20Nadu)%2C%20parts%20of%20Karnataka%2C%20and%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20due%20to%20their%20suitable%20climate.%20A%20medicinal%20and%20aromatic%20plant%2C%20it%20is%20not%20eaten%20by%20animals%20and%20rarely%20attacked%20by%20pests.%20Its%20leaves%20start%20to%20grow%20shortly%20after%20harvest%2C%20and%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F403491%2Fharyana-techie-and-wife-launch-successful-morina-business-organic-farming-improving-health%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20farmers%20can%20easily%20earn%20more%20profit%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGeranium%20is%20valued%20for%20its%20leaves%2C%20which%20are%20processed%20to%20extract%20essential%20oil.%20This%20oil%20is%20in%20high%20demand%20both%20in%20India%20and%20internationally.%20Once%20planted%2C%20geranium%20can%20be%20harvested%20four%20times%20a%20year%20for%20about%20four%20years%2C%20yielding%2015%E2%80%9316%20tons%20of%20leaves%20every%20three%20months.%20Geranium%20plants%20require%20less%20irrigation%20making%20them%20a%20practical%20alternative%20to%20traditional%20crops%20like%20paddy%20and%20pulses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20870px)%20100vw%2C%20870px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FThe-Patade-family-1_10_11zon-1751287674.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22870%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Geranium%20farming%20in%20Chhattisgarh%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FThe-Patade-family-1_10_11zon-1751287674.jpg%20870w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FThe-Patade-family-1_10_11zon-1751287674-300x208.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FThe-Patade-family-1_10_11zon-1751287674-500x347.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FThe-Patade-family-1_10_11zon-1751287674-768x533.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FThe-Patade-family-1_10_11zon-1751287674-150x104.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-458386%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22604%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ELokesh%E2%80%99s%20fields%20yield%20up%20to%2050%E2%80%9360%20litres%20of%20oil%20per%20acre%20each%20year%2C%20and%20the%20plant%E2%80%99s%20natural%20resistance%20to%20pests%20means%20lower%20costs.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20resident%20of%20Bilaspur%2C%20Patade%20cultivates%20geranium%E2%80%94the%20Egyptian%20variety%20(Pelargonium%20graveolens)%20also%20called%20the%20Kelkar%20variety%E2%80%94on%20three%20acres%20of%20land%2C%20at%20Rs%2080%2C000%20per%20acre.%20Harvested%20every%20third%20or%20fourth%20month%2C%20a%20geranium%20plant%20continued%20to%20produce%20leaves%20for%20three%20to%20four%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETraining%20farmers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20various%20medicinal%20and%20aromatic%20plants%20like%20lemongrass%20and%20palmarosa%20were%20already%20being%20cultivated%20in%20his%20region%2C%20geranium%20was%20largely%20unknown%20to%20local%20farmers.%20Geranium%20is%20widely%20grown%20both%20in%20India%20and%20abroad%2C%20and%2C%20like%20other%20aromatic%20plants%2C%20its%20essential%20oil%20can%20be%20refined%20and%20has%20a%20strong%20market%20demand%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Patade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeadow%20Agrotech%2C%20is%20an%20incubated%20startup%20of%20IGKV%20RABI%2C%20(Indira%20Gandhi%20Krishi%20Vishwavidyalaya%20%E2%80%93%20Research%20and%20Business%20Incubation)%2C%20located%20in%20Raipur%2C%20Chhattisgarh.%20An%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F391351%2Fsarbeswar-basumatary-padma-shri-assam-agriculture-journey%2F%5C%22%3Eagricultural%20innovation%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20business%20incubation%20hub%2C%20it%20supports%20startups%20and%20entrepreneurs%20in%20the%20agri-business%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20300px)%20100vw%2C%20300px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FGeranium-saplings_3_11zon-1751287642.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Geranium%20farming%20in%20Chhattisgarh%5C%22%20src