20water%20distillation.%20When%20geranium%20leaves%20and%20flowers%20are%20distilled%2C%20steam%20passes%20through%20the%20plant%20matter%2C%20extracting%20aromatic%20and%20bioactive%20compounds.%20The%20resulting%20vapor%20is%20then%20condensed%2C%20separating%20into%20two%20main%20products%3A%20essential%20oil%20(the%20oil-soluble%20fraction)%20and%20hydrosol%20(the%20water-soluble%20fraction).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOrganic%20air%20freshener%20that%20encourages%20sustainable%20farming%20and%20reduces%20waste%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatade%E2%80%99s%20geranium%20hydrosol%20air%20fresheners%E2%80%94available%20in%20200ml%20cans%20on%20e-commerce%20sites%E2%80%94offer%20a%20natural%2C%20eco-friendly%20alternative%20to%20chemical%20sprays.%20Made%20from%20the%20byproduct%20of%20geranium%20oil%20extraction%2C%20they%20provide%20a%20sweet%2C%20floral%20aroma%20that%20uplifts%20mood%20and%20reduces%20stress.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hydrosol%E2%80%99s%20natural%20antibacterial%20and%20antimicrobial%20properties%20help%20purify%20air%20and%20surfaces%2C%20while%20its%20scent%20repels%20insects%2C%20making%20it%20both%20pleasant%20and%20practical.%20Free%20from%20synthetic%20additives%2C%20these%20air%20fresheners%20are%20safe%20for%20children%20and%20pets.%20By%20utilizing%20a%20byproduct%2C%20they%20also%20support%20sustainable%20farming%20and%20reduce%20waste%2C%20offering%20gentle%20therapeutic%20benefits%20for%20both%20people%20and%20the%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FTechie-Earthworms-1751288015.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Geranium%20farming%20in%20Chhattisgarh%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FTechie-Earthworms-1751288015.jpg%201200w%