t%20the%20site%2C%20and%20this%20job%20was%20created%20because%20of%20this%20project.%20I%20can%20earn%20and%20support%20my%20family%20now.%20We%20also%20feel%20blessed%20to%20breathe%20clean%20air%20and%20drink%20water%20that%20is%20not%20polluted%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20women%20like%20Pranali%20and%20Geeta%2C%20this%20project%20is%20more%20than%20just%20a%20green%20belt.%20%3Cstrong%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20lifeline%E2%80%94a%20place%20that%20gave%20them%20back%20their%20dignity%2C%20their%20health%2C%20and%20their%20ability%20to%20provide%20for%20their%20families.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20once%20was%20written%20off%20as%20useless%20land%20is%20now%20a%20living%2C%20breathing%20space%20where%20women%20work%2C%20crops%20grow%2C%20and%20children%20play%20in%20the%20fresh%20air%E2%80%94proof%20that%20when%20science%20and%20community%20come%20together%2C%20even%20the%20most%20broken%20places%20can%20bloom%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20ERT%20Works%3A%20Science%20Behind%20the%20Green%20Transformation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Eco-Rejuvenation%20Technology%20is%20an%20eco-friendly%2C%20cost-effective%20solution%20developed%20by%20CSIR-NEERI%20(Council%20of%20Scientific%20and%20Industrial%20Research%20%E2%80%93%20National%20Environmental%20Engineering%20Research%20Institute).%20It%20was%20designed%20to%20restore%20and%20rejuvenate%20degraded%20or%20contaminated%20lands%2C%20particularly%20those%20affected%20by%20fly%20ash%2C%20heavy%20metals%2C%20or%20industrial%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-24_11zon-1751358687.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Singh%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFrom%20cleaning%20the%20land%20to%20watering%20the%20bamboo%20trees%20and%20taking