%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhile%20working%20in%20a%20highly%20reputable%20private%20hospital%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Dr%20S%20M%20Ziaur%20Rahman%20encountered%20an%20impoverished%20patient%20from%20Bihar%20%E2%80%94%20tired%2C%20anxious%2C%20and%20far%20from%20home.%20That%20meeting%20would%20go%20on%20to%20alter%20not%20just%20two%20lives%2C%20but%20the%20very%20landscape%20of%20healthcare%20in%20the%20village%20he%20had%20once%20left%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20met%20a%20patient%20whose%20blood%20pressure%20was%2020%2F150.%20During%20our%20conversation%2C%20he%20mentioned%20that%20he%20came%20from%20a%20rural%20area%20that%20lacked%20access%20to%20doctors.%20I%20got%20curious%20about%20his%20background%2C%20so%20I%20asked%20him%20more%20about%20where%20he%20was%20from.%20To%20my%20surprise%2C%20he%20said%20Khagaria%20%E2%80%94%20my%20own%20district%20in%20Bihar.%20That%20patient%20had%20come%20all%20the%20way%20from%20Bihar%20to%20Delhi%20%5B1%2C200%20kilometres%5D%20just%20for%20the%20treatment%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20revelation%20shook%20him.%20%E2%80%9CDespite%20the%20presence%20of%20world-class%20medical%20care%20in%20places%20like%20Delhi%2C%20there%20was%20still%20a%20lack%20of%20adequate%20services%20in%20my%20region.%20This%20experience%20lit%20a%20spark%20in%20me%20%E2%80%94%20a%20determination%20to%20work%20in%20my%20hometown%20and%20improve%20healthcare%20access%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Dr%20Rahman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20Dr%20Rahman%20was%20working%20in%20the%20non-invasive%20cardiac%20department%20and%20had%20a%20clear%20path%20ahead%3A%20a%20stable%2C%20high-paying%20career%20in%20the%20city.%20But%20that%20single%20conversation%20awakened%20something%20deeper%20%E2%80%94%20a%20pull%20towards%20home%2C%20where%20healthcare%20was%20not%20a%20business%2C%20but%20a%20lifeline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20cities%2C%20healthcare%20is%20business%3B%20back%20home%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20survival%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20That%20became%20the%20cornerstone%20of%20his%20mission%3A%20to%20provide%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F291947%2Fdelhi-doctor-neurologist-quits-united-states-job-give-affordable-healthcare-to-rural-bihar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccessible%20healthcare%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20the%20people%20of%20his%20hometown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fdoctors-day-2-1751290124.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Rahman%20runs%20the%20National%20Medicare%20Hospital%20%26amp%3B%20Research%20Centre%20in%20Khagaria.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fdoctors-day-2-1751290124.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fdoctors-day-2-1751290124-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fdoctors-day-2-1751290124-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fdoctors-day-2-1751290124-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fdoctors-day-2-1751290124-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-458461%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Rahman%20runs%20the%20National%20Medicare%20Hospital%20%26amp%3B%20Research%20Centre%20in%20Khagaria.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAn%20innocent%20childhood%20promise%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Rahman%20was%20born%20into%20an%20impoverished%20farmer%20family%20in%20a%20small%20village%20in%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%C2%A0Khagaria%20district.%20His%20father%20owned%20about%20five%20acres%20of%20land%20and%20three%20buffalo.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20our%20family%E2%80%99s%20only%20asset%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20despite%20our%20circumstances%2C%20my%20father%20never%20once%20insisted%20that%20I%20take%20on%20the%20responsibilities%20of%20farming%20or%20tending%20to%20the%20buffalo.%20Even%20my%20mother%20never%20forced%20me%20to%20go%20to%20the%20flour%20mill%20to%20grind%20grains.%20Instead%2C%20my%20parents%20encouraged%20me%20to%20focus%20on%20my%20education.%20They%20placed%20all%20their%20faith%20in%20my%20education%2C%20and%20I%20never%20wanted%20to%20betray%20that%20trust.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Rahman%20was%20just%20a%20child%20when%20he%20learnt%20one%20of%20life%E2%80%99s%20harshest%20lessons.%20Once%2C%20he%20accompanied%20his%20ailing%20mother%20and%20younger%20brother%20to%20a%20hospital.%20They%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20afford%20to%20pay%20for%20two%20separate%20consultations%2C%20which%20led%20to%20humiliation%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20a%20compounder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20about%20five%20or%20six%20years%20old%20when%20my%20mother%20took%20me%20and%20my%20younger%20brother%20to%20a%20hospital.%20We%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20enough%20money%2C%20so%20she%20asked%20the%20compounder%20if%20both%20of%20us%20could%20be%20treated%20under%20the%20same%20prescription%20to%20save%20money.%20He%20reacted%20harshly%2C%20scolding%20us%20for%20being%20poor.%20I%20was%20too%20young%20to%20understand%20everything%2C%20but%20I%20remember%20the%20shame%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20doctor%2C%20whom%20I%20revered%20and%20still%20consider%20my%20role%20model%2C%20was%20compassionate%20and%20did%20not%20treat%20us%20poorly.%20This%20experience%20stayed%20with%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20indignity%20of%20being%20scolded%20for%20poverty%20became%20a%20turning%20point%20in%20Dr%20Rahman%E2%80%99s%20life%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that%20shaped%20his%20resolve%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F398655%2Fdr-taru-jindal-doctor-improving-bihar-healthcare-district-hospital-maternal-care%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etransform%20healthcare%20for%20the%20underprivileged%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9COne%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20vowed%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20will%20become%20a%20doctor%20who%20never%20turns%20anyone%20away%20for%20lack%20of%20money.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fdoctors-day-3-1751290132.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Rahman%20offers%20regular%20check-ups%20as%20well%20as%20emergency%20services.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fdoctors-day-3-1751290132.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fdoctors-day-3-1751290132-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fdoctors-day-3-1751290132-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fdoctors-day-3-1751290132-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fdoctors-day-3-1751290132-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-458462%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Rahman%20offers%20regular%20check-ups%20as%20well%20as%20emergency%20services.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20incident%20that%20further%20pushed%20him%20towards%20his%20goal%20came%20in%20school%2C%20when%20his%20biology%20teacher%20asked%20a%20question%20in%20class.%20Dr%20Rahman%20answered%20it%20instantly.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20blessed%20me%20and%20sa