%9D%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Pushpa%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20worry%20is%20child%20marriage.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20stop%20this%20from%20happening.%20At%20least%20through%20education%20and%20sports%2C%20I%20feel%20we%20can%20help%20girls%20escape%20early%20marriages%20and%20other%20unhappy%20futures%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pushpa%20adds.%20And%20she%20believes%20that%20Mitti%20Ka%20Ghar%20will%20edify%20this%20hope%20for%20them.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArchitect%20Sourabh%20Gujar%20(32)%20shares%20this%20belief.%20He%20is%20among%20the%20team%20of%20people%20restoring%20the%20school%20to%20its%20former%20glory.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fsustainable-school-muskaan-ngo-mitti-ka-ghar-6-1751289234.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Learning%20in%20a%20school%20that's%20built%20out%20of%20mud%20helps%20children%20feel%20comfortable%20as%20it%20mimics%20their%20home%20settings%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fsustainable-school-muskaan-ngo-mitti-ka-ghar-6-1751289234.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fsustainable-school-muskaan-ngo-mitti-ka-ghar-6-1751289234-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fsustainable-school-muskaan-ngo-mitti-ka-ghar-6-1751289234-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fsustainable-school-muskaan-ngo-mitti-ka-ghar-6-1751289234-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fsustainable-school-muskaan-ngo-mitti-ka-ghar-6-1751289234-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-458432%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigca